channel.title: Grab All Runescape Models
channel.description:
Hi, I've just edited this thread to have a more specific question:
Since apparently, RSMV is not functional anymore, could someone please help me get all of the Runescape current models? I want to add some items in to my 317 client but I need the models first which I can not find a method to do so.
If there is no a practical way to get all of the newer models (for a beginner who is experimenting with adding items to a server), could someone please link me to a file or an area where there are a lot of pre-grabbed models that may not be entirely up to date but atleast close?
Thanks, any help is appreciated!
